<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v3" title="Red de buses y ecuacion lineal" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En el diseño de una red de buses urbanos, se establece que para ciertos diseños se cumple la relación <m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>I</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, donde <em>R</em> es el número de recorridos, <em>T</em> es el número de terminales y <em>I</em> es el número de intersecciones importantes del sistema.</p>
    <p>En un cierto diseño se cuentan 5 recorridos y 21 intersecciones importantes, y se sabe que cumple con la relación anterior. ¿Cuántos terminales tiene ese diseño?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">16<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si T = 16, entonces R + T = 5 + 16 = 21. Pero I + 2 = 21 + 2 = 23. Como 21 ≠ 23, esta opción no satisface la relación.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">18<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si T = 18, entonces R + T = 5 + 18 = 23. Además, I + 2 = 21 + 2 = 23. Como ambos lados son iguales a 23, esta opción satisface la relación.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">24<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si T = 24, entonces R + T = 5 + 24 = 29. Pero I + 2 = 21 + 2 = 23. Como 29 ≠ 23, esta opción no cumple la relación dada.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">28<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si T = 28, entonces R + T = 5 + 28 = 33. Pero I + 2 = 21 + 2 = 23. Como 33 ≠ 23, esta opción no cumple la relación dada.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la relación del problema</strong></p>
            <p>Se cumple:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>R</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>I</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar los datos conocidos</strong></p>
            <p>El diseño tiene 5 recorridos y 21 intersecciones importantes, por lo tanto:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>21</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Simplificar el lado derecho</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>21</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces la ecuación queda:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar el número de terminales</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 5 en ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Verificar</strong></p>
            <p>Si <m:math><m:mi>T</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>y</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>21</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>23</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Ambos lados son iguales, así que la respuesta es correcta.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El diseño tiene <strong>18 terminales</strong>. La alternativa correcta es <strong>B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>